FBIS3-33551 "drlat038_b_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-038 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Feb 1994 Haiti Belizaire Opposes Embargo, Asks That `Vacuum' Be Filled FL2402224194 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio in French 1130 GMT 24 Feb 94 FL2402224194 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio Language: French Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Senator Dejean Belizaire says no to the embargo and condemns those who are asking for reinforcement of the sanctions against Haiti at this critical stage of the situation. Sen. Belizaire asks the officials to fill the power vacuum for a final solution to the crisis. [passage omitted]
